      <title>美国考虑对中国获取人工智能内存芯片实施新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-weighs-new-restrictions-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正考虑最早于下个月对中国获取人工智能存储芯片以及能够生产这些半导体的设备实施单方面限制，此举将进一步加剧世界最大经济体之间的技术竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-weighs-new-restrictions-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 17:41:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
