      <title>英特尔将裁员数千人以降低成本、推动基金反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/intel-to-cut-thousands-of-jobs-to-reduce-costs-fund-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司计划裁员数千人，以降低成本，并为摆脱盈利下滑和市场份额损失的困境筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/intel-to-cut-thousands-of-jobs-to-reduce-costs-fund-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 21:14:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裁员 6% 且盈利情况乐观，Match 股价创 2022 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/match-group-s-tinder-payer-decline-worsens-amid-activist-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Match Group Inc. 宣布计划裁员 6% 并公布好于预期的收益后，其股价创下近两年来最大涨幅，这向华尔街投资者发出信号，最糟糕的时期可能已经过去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/match-group-s-tinder-payer-decline-worsens-amid-activist-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
